  "description": "<p>最近HTC高管出现了频繁的跳槽，其中主要原因是智能手机出货量低于预期，此外窘迫的财政状况导致HTC高管的收入大幅缩水。<strong>根据HTC今天公布的年度报 告中显示HTC现在高管总的支付薪水为2194万美元，而2011年4518万美元的支出缩水了51.4%。此外公司CEO周永明和现任总工程师Fred Lui在两年内首次突破330万<strong>美元</strong>。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2da0f41f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242081.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E4%B8%BA2194%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%8311%E5%B9%B4%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B451.4%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242081.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E4%B8%BA2194%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%8311%E5%B9%B4%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B451.4%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242081.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E4%B8%BA2194%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%8311%E5%B9%B4%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B451.4%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242081.htm&amp;t=HTC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E4%B8%BA2194%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%8311%E5%B9%B4%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B451.4%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img